    <string name="about_legal_heading">Legal disclaimer</string>
    <string name="about_legal_body">Release templates are generic wording samples for convenience. They are not attorney-reviewed contracts, not official forms of any stock agency or platform, and not legal advice. Have counsel review language for your jurisdiction before commercial use.</string>
    <string name="about_privacy_heading">Privacy</string>
    <string name="about_privacy_body">ReleaseCanvas works offline for core signing. Optional GPS and reverse geocode use device location services and may use network. PDFs are written to Documents/ReleaseCanvas via MediaStore. History is stored only on this device. Optional cloud copies use the system share sheet (e.g. Drive, Dropbox) under your account — there is no automatic cloud sync and no ReleaseCanvas server.</string>
    <string name="about_license_heading">License</string>
